&lt;p&gt;We’re on a mission to become the go-to destination for students across Europe to find a trusted home away from home. We make every step of the rental journey simple and seamless, so students can focus on what really matters: studying, exploring, and growing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With HousingAnywhere, Kamernet, and Studapart under our roof, we’re Europe’s largest student rental platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll find us in Rotterdam, Paris, and Cergy, always guided by our four core values: Ownership, We are enablers, We are changemakers, and We are connectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us in empowering students to unlock their potential through a safe, online, rental experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Business Development Representative (BDR) for the Private Landlord market, your primary mission is to expand HousingAnywhere&#39;s inventory by actively hunting and onboarding new property owners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Private Landlord team is a key driver of our marketplate’s growth and is now expanding. We are looking for a new Business Development Representative to own the German market growth end-to-end. This role requires an entrepreneurial mindset, combining high-volume phone outreach with a data-driven approach to identify opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outbound Acquisition:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify, prospect, and acquire new private landlords primarily through cold calling and proactive outreach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End Onboarding:&lt;/strong&gt; Educate landlords on product features, supporting them closely until they successfully score their first booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expectation &amp;amp; Objection Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Confidently handle complex landlord objections while maintaining a professional partnership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Success &amp;amp; Revenue Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Train landlords to use the product effectively to maximize their occupancy and revenue, while driving commercial growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Relationship Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Build strong, long-term relationships with landlords, acting as their trusted point of contact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven City Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor your local portfolio performance, analyze the data and take action to improve your metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Advocacy &amp;amp; Problem Solving:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain a sharp eye for product issues in the user journey and proactively share actionable feedback.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner closely with Product and Customer Success teams to continuously elevate the landlord experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovation:&lt;/strong&gt; Proactively identify and support opportunities to improve processes through automation and AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Native&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;German&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and fluent in English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hunter Mentality: &lt;/strong&gt;Proven experience or strong comfort with high-volume cold calling and managing a pipeline from scratch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commercial Polish:&lt;/strong&gt; Excellent communication skills to negotiate and build trust over the phone.&lt;/li&gt;
